Title: Part 8
Writer: Mark Frost, David Lynch, David Lynch (creator), Mark Frost (creator)
Actors: Kyle MacLachlan, Leslie Berger, Robert Broski, Cullen Douglas
Plot: Cooper's doppelganger faces a life-or-death situation. In 1945, the Trinity atomic bomb test in White Sands, New Mexico leads to horrifying unexpected consequences. In 1956, a creepy woodsman covered in scorched engine oil invades a radio station.
